bpedia.org/resource/Mick_Jagger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mick_Jagger\"}, {\"begin\": 116, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.682316280630192e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stars opted for black and white colours for the event, called the Prelude to the Olympics, which took place at the 6th arrondissement museum, the Louis Vuitton Foundation.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton_Foundation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton Foundation\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton_Foundation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was co-hosted byMad Max: Fury Roadstar and South African actress Theron, wearing a white one-shoulder dress, along withLupinstar and French actor Omar Sy, US tennis star Serena Williams and Spanish singer Rosalia.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cavalera\", \"score\": 0.9373647562629495, \"rank\": 0.06655059353197905, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cavalera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cavalera\"}, {\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erinyes\", \"score\": 0.9997086482131302, \"rank\": 0.00029143669727517413, \"text\": \"Fury\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erinyes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erinyes\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roadstar\", \"score\": 0.9957635203281795